{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","title":"setUserId:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"userId"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"completion"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username)."}]}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setUserId:"},{"text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"title":"setUserId:completion:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind"